@startuml GU43
actor Administrator

participant "View" as View
participant "Routes" as Routes
participant "PermissionsMiddleware" as Mid
participant "PermissionsController" as Controller
participant "AuthUseCase" as AuthUseCase
participant "PermissionsUseCase" as UseCase
participant "PermissionsEntity" as PermissionsEntity
participant "ExceptionsEntity" as ExceptionsEntity
participant "PermissionsDTO" as PermissionsDTO
participant "ExceptionsDTO" as ExceptionsDTO
participant "PermissionsRepository" as Repository
database "DB" as DB

Administrator -> View : Selecciona usuario y presiona "Ver permisos"

View -> Routes : GET /api/admin/users/:userId/permissions

Routes -> Mid : requirePermission('Permissions', 'consultation')

Mid -> AuthUseCase : checkPermission(adminId, 'Permissions', 'consultation')

alt administrador autorizado

```
Mid --> Routes : authorized

Routes -> Controller : getPermission(userId)

Controller -> UseCase : execute({ userId })

par Obtener permisos ACL

    UseCase -> Repository : fetchAll({ userId })

    Repository -> DB : SELECT user_acl + modules
    DB --> Repository : permissionsData[]

    Repository --> UseCase : permissionsData[]

and Obtener privilegios base

    UseCase -> Repository : fetchPrivilegeNames()

    Repository -> DB : SELECT privilege_role + privilege
    DB --> Repository : exceptionsData[]

    Repository --> UseCase : exceptionsData[]

end

UseCase -> PermissionsEntity : new Permissions({ permissionsData })
PermissionsEntity --> UseCase : permissionsEntity

UseCase -> ExceptionsEntity : new Exceptions({ exceptionsData })
ExceptionsEntity --> UseCase : exceptionsEntity

UseCase --> Controller : {\npermissions,\nexceptions\n}

Controller -> PermissionsDTO : fromEntity(permissions)
PermissionsDTO --> Controller : permissionsDto

Controller -> ExceptionsDTO : fromEntity(exceptions)
ExceptionsDTO --> Controller : exceptionsDto

Controller --> Routes : HTTP 200

Routes --> View : {\n permissions,\n exceptions\n}

View --> Administrator : Mostrar matriz de permisos\n y excepciones
```

else administrador sin permisos

```
Mid --> Routes : HTTP 403
Routes --> View : Error
View --> Administrator : No autorizado
```

end

@enduml
